{"tid":1412553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8/8 海港城】 Weekday 升級支援方案 『和理非』都可輕鬆參與！（續）第一波","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:25:06.000Z","uid":36432,"like":64,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cbbe1f3eed3afd25102a03d9406ce350ecd31c","tid":1412553,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"因為個post推唔起，我再開多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />～ 「開心個人遊商場-第一波」，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">星期四（8/8）自己去海港城行街</span></ins></span>食嘢嘅攻略，如果TLDR嘅，不妨Follow返 <a href=\"https://t.me/trybeforeyoubuy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftrybeforeyoubuy&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=256ba534\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/trybeforeyoubuy</a>， 拎住最新資訊❤️做個精明消費者。<br />\n<br />\n 行街原因可以睇返：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1391869/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1391869/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzwFjq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzwFjq.png&h=05dbbca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抱住「<ins><strong>開心個人遊商場</strong></ins>」出去時，以下係一啲參考資料。<br />\n香港打工仔工時長，學生哥讀書壓力大，行街係一個好好嘅解壓活動！同埋身為環保份子，夏天咁L熱梗係自己行商場涼下冷氣啦，仲可以幫商場刺激人流𠻹。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行商場有咩用？</span></span>。 <br />\n商場人流多就當然好， 但人流多到水洩不通導至商場接應不暇，咁商家要自己諗方法解決，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但如果商家生意上持續有困難，商家就要快啲向<ins><ins>政府表達取消某啲極具爭議性同影響力嘅政策[</ins>/gold]</ins>。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解行海港城？</span></span><br />\n除咗交通方便，有船/巴/地鐵外，海港城亦有種類繁多嘅店舖，滿足晒每個人嘅需要。更重要一點，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">海港城有好多內地旅客，自發行街嘅你，要多啲同遊客溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁大個商場行邊好先？</span></span><br />\n入去TG@trybeforeyoubuy有星級推薦名單俾大家😀，自發活動，大家去邊都得架👍。提一提，千祈唔好三四個人喺商戶門口堵路，因為咁樣人哋就做唔到生意，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住，&quot;千祈千祈唔好&quot;塞住個門囗呀。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如想支持本土小店？</span></span></span><br />\n行到肚餓，巴絲可以<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出去小店買嘢醫肚</span></strong></ins>。口乾呢，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以去商場內餐廳飲返杯，根據英國研究飲水係最解渴</span>！<br />\n買嘢方面，記得試多d，貨比三家，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">試過唔岩就唔好強求喇🤡</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要黑衫，口罩？</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一個個人，自發嘅行動</span></strong>，無須Dress Code。不過空氣唔好戴個口罩都好合理🤡。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會犯法嗎？</span></span><br />\n行商場絕對冇犯法，幫商場增加人流出師有名。慢慢行慢慢睇，又唔會造成財物損失，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做個精明嘅</span>消/<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[gold]不消費者</span></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs8hByL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs8hByL.png&h=1db2077d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjYtJdL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjYtJdL.png&h=72e38302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJpD5sJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJpD5sJ.png&h=29a437e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rWnNF3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rWnNF3.png&h=2c09a91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望星期四可以行得開心，玩得放心啦。🥳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🔥五大訴求 缺一不可🔥<br />\n✨光復香港 時代革命✨</span>"},{"pid":"ea0ff3ec8bb944873ec007f1345206c902a2f966","tid":1412553,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:03:19.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"d69d9553f6b6ce26f0f72bc22ea0a576caf4ed73","tid":1412553,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"你今日罷咗未"},{"pid":"722152271428f1ff4ebd013407dbf6060d0bd4c6","tid":1412553,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce53ab6b4899c21012ef7689728f31dec9f184a3","tid":1412553,"uid":261705,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"唔買會畀人鬧運吉<br />\n識玩梗係入toyrus排兩粒鐘買粒糖"},{"pid":"02b454b9049dccaa70dd66bc4a11c1b5bfc0bfa9","tid":1412553,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2260a564b365ab95c06e768cb62dcb24626db4e4","tid":1412553,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b1b5dd6f6a1a79cce9a2020c43d1168e17a384ab","tid":1412553,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"661c41bcd35de916b50a24c827185f5e2a555de2","tid":1412553,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a91623c781cd398635b1272a0c8c4b962290713","tid":1412553,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce53ab6b4899c21012ef7689728f31dec9f184a3","tid":1412553,"uid":261705,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"唔買會畀人鬧運吉<br />\n識玩梗係入toyrus排兩粒鐘買粒糖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"個人行動嘅嘢自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d73ddb240a49d4e50715e58d54a4c30b5075d6","tid":1412553,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94dfff91745721bae4730a190ffeabc8fd6187ae",